{"tid":1570154,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"勇武係劍，和理非係盾！勇武唔需要做埋盾！想退請即退！","createTime":"2019-09-15T02:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T03:38:17.000Z","uid":321579,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"62692a130dd7469dd24ec2d14d69d4246610527a","tid":1570154,"uid":321579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:39:14.000Z","msg":"好多時見到有人話啲後排和理非冇危機感之類<br />\n有冇諗過唔敢衝嘅和理非點解要企後面？係為咗確保前線退路啊<br />\n即是話，前線想退，和理非都會即退<br />\n尤其冇gear嗰啲更加可以即時混入人群<br />\n所以，<strong>前線退嘅時候，通知後排即可，唔使下下話要幫手頂住前面</strong><br />\n<br />\n特別而家狗喺港島愈玩愈熟<br />\n金鐘退到銅鑼灣就出臥底<br />\n再成堆狗喺北角湧現包抄<br />\n散水嘅時間比以前更加少<br />\n覺得要走就唔該即走<br />\n你一話走，後排和理非走得快過你好多<br />\n<br />\n當然有樣嘢後排和理非要謹記嘅係：<br />\n<strong>企鬆啲</strong>"},{"pid":"e3c8d5eade32b10094c20ae53bcb0f406a63e45c","tid":1570154,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:39:33.000Z","msg":"Stand with HK, Anti-totalitarianism March on 29/9/2019<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1569667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1569667</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"56562f0f5d44f6ccb854564526bb42f93ffb443f","tid":1570154,"uid":27647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:40:19.000Z","msg":"仆街芒"},{"pid":"7d8b8d351abe6bcf10ae1bf8dcd4f840a7bba59a","tid":1570154,"uid":144084,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvuKD9R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvuKD9R.png&h=123e34e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n殺警都唔割"},{"pid":"86dd990d2454383f46593ee562a8564230130615","tid":1570154,"uid":216683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:43:10.000Z","msg":"理應係和理非支援撤退嘅勇武<br />\n宜家掉撚返轉<br />\n要勇武守住等和理非走先<br />\n<br />\n講真你用機會成本計<br />\n勇武俾人搵vs和理非俾人拉<br />\n勇武重要過和理非好多"},{"pid":"3b2cd2944b3db09b96dc2732e4ac3d065eff9f0a","tid":1570154,"uid":216664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT